OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772100321
OL,3,CPortsmouth man who ran network
OL,4,Csmuggling illegal migrants into UK
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA prolific people smuggler responsible
OL,8,Ffor transporting hundreds of illegal
OL,9,Fmigrants to the UK has been jailed,
OL,10,Fthe National Crime Agency (NCA) said.
OL,12,FAli Omar Karim, who smuggled people to
OL,13,Fthe country via small boats and HGVs,
OL,14,Fwas jailed for eight years and seven
OL,15,Fmonths on Wednesday at Maidstone Crown
OL,16,FCourt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
