PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772100321
OL,3,CPortsmouth man who ran network
OL,4,Csmuggling illegal migrants into UK
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FOfficers identified him after a yacht
OL,8,Fran aground in Rye, East Sussex, and
OL,9,FCCTV showed people jumping from the
OL,10,Fvessel and swimming to shore while
OL,11,Fothers travelled in a dinghy before
OL,12,Ffleeing across land, the agency said.
OL,14,FSome 14 individuals from Iran, Iraq
OL,15,Fand Albania, including two children,
OL,16,Fwere then detained within two hours by
OL,17,FBorder Force officers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
