OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772100321
OL,3,CPortsmouth man who ran network
OL,4,Csmuggling illegal migrants into UK
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe NCA said its investigation
OL,8,Funcovered Karim was in control of a
OL,9,Fnetwork of people smugglers across
OL,10,Fnorthern Europe and the Middle East.
OL,12,FEvidence on the 47-year-old's phone
OL,13,Fsuggested people that were trafficked
OL,14,Fpaid between #800 to #1,000 to get
OL,15,Finto the EU before paying a larger
OL,16,Famount to travel onwards from France
OL,17,Fto the UK, according to the agency.
OL,19,FMessages revealed Karim had discussed
OL,20,Fcharging migrants #1,650 each for a
OL,21,Fcrossing in an HGV in November 2022.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772100321
OL,3,CPortsmouth man who ran network
OL,4,Csmuggling illegal migrants into UK
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA lorry was stopped in Calais on
OL,8,FNovember 17 2022 and two Iraqi
OL,9,Fnationals where found hidden inside
OL,10,Fthe trailer.
OL,12,FFurther evidence showed Karim, from
OL,13,FPortsmouth, had also been involved in
OL,14,Forganising fake visas so that people
OL,15,Fcould travel by plane, the NCA said.
OL,17,FHe was arrested in Portsmouth in March
OL,18,F2024 and pleaded guilty to people
OL,19,Fsmuggling offences in June that year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
