FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772100321
OL,3,CPortsmouth man who ran network
OL,4,Csmuggling illegal migrants into UK
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FNCA branch commander Rachel Bramley
OL,8,Fsaid: "Karim was a key member of an
OL,9,Forganised crime group involved in
OL,10,Ftransporting people by HGV, small
OL,11,Fboat, yachts and planes.
OL,13,F"He was high up in the chain of
OL,14,Fcommand, making decisions on crossing
OL,15,Fdays, routes and prices.
OL,17,F"This was a long-running NCA
OL,18,Finvestigation working alongside
OL,19,Fpartners in the UK and overseas.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
