OL,3,CPortsmouth man who ran network
OL,4,Csmuggling illegal migrants into UK
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"Tackling organised immigration crime
OL,8,Fis a top priority for the NCA and we
OL,9,Fare doing all we can to target,
OL,10,Fdisrupt and dismantle the criminal
OL,11,Fnetworks behind it, wherever they
OL,12,Foperate."
